### HYMN CXIII

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2011301">1</span></span>Both
boons—may Indra hitherward turned, listen to this, prayer  
   of ours,  
  And, mightiest Maghavan with thought inclined to us come nigh  
   to drink the Soma juice.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2011302">2</span></span>For him,
strong independent Ruler, Heaven and Earth have  
   fashioned forth for power and might.  
  Thou seatest thee as first among thy peers in place, for thy soul  
   longs for Soma juice.

